

Run
`npx prisma generate`
to generate the models on change.

You can split schemas specifically yourself - if you don't want them to be shared.
You can create "frontend.schema.prisma"
```
generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
  output   = "../frontend/src/generated/prisma"
}
```

This will create the models in "../frontend/src/generated/prisma" instead of shared.